{"tid":1306790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理性分析被打：唔擋、擋、還擊？","createTime":"2019-07-11T09:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T10:54:29.000Z","uid":274055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ba66449522131f1c543f19f01a28e83563ab6e","tid":1306790,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:40:16.000Z","msg":"尊重麥生去做沙包/擋箭牌。宜家講乜都係馬後炮，不過分析下下次應該點理性應付：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190711/59811463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F59811463&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852yEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=a736691c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F59811463&h=89fb8aa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190711/59811463</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">「要毋忘初衷，唔好為幅牆而有人受傷」</code></pre><br />\n正正係爲咗減少受傷，要用其他部位（例如手）去擋，唔係暴露最易受傷嘅部位去擋（= 唔擋）。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">「唔係話避就避到，可能避會產生其他後果。」</code></pre><br />\n如果避可能會打落其他人度，咁擋就唔會。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">「大家都係為咗香港，不想任何人受傷，如果當時還手可能會傷及其他人。」</code></pre><br />\n唔還手攻擊去自衛，又有能力擋得到，各方受傷就會最少，對方又唔會得逞教訓到人。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">學習跆拳道是為了強身健體，在遇到危險時能保護自己。</code></pre><br />\n所以 <strong><ins>唔擋、擋、還擊</ins></strong> 之間應該選擇用防禦姿勢去擋到警察嚟到。<br />\n擋唔到嘅人應該撤離避開。"},{"pid":"ecc66b686203d3b33b2fb93c5ea7b75f31c61849","tid":1306790,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bNFY6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bNFY6E.jpg&h=0e3ff068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POJqqMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOJqqMr.jpg&h=d5937562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUnCgTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUnCgTg.jpg&h=4d401a96&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KAgxru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KAgxru.jpg&h=a97e178b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmUtoye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmUtoye.jpg&h=36d1db08&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gBzi6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gBzi6w.jpg&h=067ee06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求，不撤不散︰<br />\n<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫暴<br />\n五、實行真雙普選"},{"pid":"0d9a5dbed86604e43b6c53d3f4fc60a5b3b1b508","tid":1306790,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"係囉，防暴警嚟打嚟噴椒都會擋啊～"},{"pid":"a44e9ce8bb258da78cbbf741fa7ba855c5d51aa6","tid":1306790,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"作用力 = 反作用力"},{"pid":"b8b1763de73a4008e9329f0e5bb9992cf634db67","tid":1306790,"uid":274055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a44e9ce8bb258da78cbbf741fa7ba855c5d51aa6","tid":1306790,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"作用力 = 反作用力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"係啊，所以做沙包都係一種擋，但最好用盾牌擋。<br />\n<br />\n擋同還擊之間 仲有制伏，但反抗得越勁就越暴力。"},{"pid":"3e677f94acdd653edfaf25ff321160e39483813a","tid":1306790,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfe465a5cb1849860efeb9aa36a5ed63b080f302","tid":1306790,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"其實由被打到打人都有不同嘅程度：<br />\n<br />\n被打 - 即係乜都唔做企喺度（唔擋）<br />\n閃避 - 令對方打唔中，只得空拳<br />\n逃走 - 離開對方攻擊範圍<br />\n擋架 - 唔閃避但儘量減少傷害<br />\n威嚇 - 作勢或警告對方停止攻擊<br />\n制伏 - 令對方冇能力攻擊<br />\n反擊 - 令對方受傷被制伏或逃走<br />\n<br />\n反擊甚至制伏都屬於暴力"},{"pid":"dc9c8665d60dc29d9617b537eb18be0d5b415bf1","tid":1306790,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"唔理你爭取咩先，你用暴力就一定錯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329809</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5fa338f92e7d911a0c064049c74ac8ec81f3b88f","tid":1306790,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"提防熱普仇城毛五派搞分化<br />\n721記得五大訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bh1sWtu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbh1sWtu.png&h=eb1b20f4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}